‼️DISCLAIMER BEFORE YOU FREAK OUT‼️
I’m not saying degrees are trash—I’m saying the system is.
Memorizing textbooks and passing exams doesn’t equal real skill.
Yeah, in fields like medicine, degrees matter—no debate.
But if you didn’t follow the “right” path, don’t count yourself out.
You don’t need a paper to prove your worth—you need clarity, skill, and fire.
Learning is 24/7. Real education is chasing curiosity, asking better questions, and building what school never taught you.
Stay hungry. Stay smart. Make your own lane.
